<h1>Make something good happen in your neighbourhood</h1>

<h2>
  Connect to like-minded people in your area
</h2>

<p>
  Tell us what you want to do in your neighbourhood, and we’ll find other people nearby who share your vision.
<p>

<p>
  We can help you come together to set up a group or club, or organise an event.
</p>

<section id="how-it-works">
  <div>
    <img src="<%= image_path 'like-not-like.svg' %>" alt="Co-op">
    <p>
      Tell us what you want to do and where you want to do it
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <img src="<%= image_path 'contact-info.svg' %>" alt="Co-op">
    <p>
      Give us your contact details
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <img src="<%= image_path 'others.svg' %>" alt="Co-op">
    <p>
      We'll put you in touch with people nearby who want the same things
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="neighbourhood-map">

  <div class="neighbourhood-where">
    <h2>
      Where do you want to make something happen?
    </h2>
    <p>
      What is your community or neighbourhood? It doesn’t have to be where you live - it’s the place you have a connection to, that you care about and want good things for.
    </p>
    <input type="text" name="" value="">
    <p class="helper-text">
      We’ll use this information to look for people nearby. We’ll always get your permission before sharing any contact details. We’ll also be in touch with you to find out more about how we can help.
    </p>
    <%= button_to 'Get started', get_started_path, class: 'btn btn-primary'%>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <h2>Why Co-op?</h2>
  <p>
    Co-op has always stood for self-help and solidarity. It’s our job to find new ways to support people, so that they can build a better world - for themselves.
  </p>
</footer>
